From 677cbe920b01fdc2f3c3c865be6b5957a6f25c02 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Filippo Luca Ferretti <filippoluca.ferretti@outlook.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:36:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] Add HIP backend abstraction layer

Introduce compile-time WP_ENABLE_HIP flag for AMD GPU support.

New files:
- hip_runtime.h: CUDA-to-HIP type/enum/macro mapping
- hip_util.cpp: HIP implementations of _f driver API wrappers

Modified files:
- cuda_util.h: conditional include of HIP or CUDA headers
- builtin.h: HIP-compatible FP16, atomics, approx math
- tile.h: HIP-compatible sync and unroll pragmas
---
